          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Corporate Political Disclosure Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill requires issuers of securities to, on an annual basis,&nbsp;publicly disclose political activity expenditures made during the previous year. The Securities and Exchange Commission must issue regulations to carry out this bill. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2019-02-07T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
